  "step_by_step_reasoning": "The user starts by requesting a new account via a portal. This request is received by API Gateway and forwarded to a Validation Lambda. The validation lambda verifies the request, sends a receipt confirmation via SES, and pushes the message to an SQS queue. The Create Lambda consumes messages from the SQS queue, interacts with AWS Organizations to provision and group the account into an active OU, uses CloudFormation to set up baselines and budgets, and triggers SES to email credentials to the developer.",
